bgtask

--------------------------------------------------
4740386b852c94464216293c46e3895de3474e16

Background task

Specialized classes provide run() and onwakeup() callbacks.

Provides daemonization control functions.
    start()
    stop()
    join()

And status functions:
    bool isup() const;
    bool isdown() const;
    bool is_ready() const;
    ko wait_ready(int secs) const;


